{{Unlicensed}}The [[Ravaging Wardog Cantina]] was a run-down cantina in the decrpit part of [[Kig Dannen Spaceport]] on the planet [[Gellefon]]. It was in this cantina that a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] met with [[Jade (mercenary)|Watcher]] after ordering seven [[Green Galaxy]] drinks and putting an end to a barfight which was caused by Watcher. During that meeting, [[Borsk Fey'lya]] pushed his way into the cantina and joined Watcher and the group of rebels.

